body_html:
Hi all,

This issue looks like it's encompassing a few different problems, some of which are workflow issues, some of which are bugs that are fixed in latest TensorBoard. So I'm going to close it.

You can pip install the latest tensorboard via pip install tensorflow-tensorboard.
If afterwards you still have issues, please open an issue at https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorboard.

body:
Hi all,

This issue looks like it's encompassing a few different problems, some of which are workflow issues, some of which are bugs that are fixed in latest TensorBoard. So I'm going to close it.

You can pip install the latest tensorboard via `pip install tensorflow-tensorboard`.
If afterwards you still have issues, please open an issue at https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorboard.
